data.description: Welcome to 5100 Torrey Lane, a beautiful home in Summerville, SC, where you will discover your own private backyard oasis. This stunning property features an in-ground pool, perfect for those hot summer days, and a backyard that is both spacious and private. Situated on a huge cul-de-sac lot, this home features a massive driveway that can easily accommodate up to 10 cars. The kitchen is open to the great room and includes gorgeous countertops, white cabinets, and brand new appliances. Boasting three large gathering areas, including a great room, formal living and dining room combo, and a large upstairs loft, it provides plenty of flexible space to make what you want. The primary suite is conveniently located on the ground floor, and upstairs, you will find three additional bedrooms andone bath, as well as an enormous loft area perfect for an in-home office or rec room. Many recent upgrades include a brand new roof in 2023 with a transferrable 50-year warranty and a new HVAC system installed in September 2022. The solar panels are also paid off, providing energy efficiency and savings. This home is perfect for those who love to entertain or just relax in their own private space. Located near one of the main entrances of Wescott; this home is conveniently located near plenty of shopping, Mercedes, Boeing, Volvo, Joint Base Charleston, and local golf courses. Don't miss your chance to own this beautiful property and make it your own!
